Class FileSubstitutionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.enterprise.admin.servermgmt.stringsubs.impl.FileSubstitutionHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Substitutable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LargeFileSubstitutionHandler, SmallFileSubstitutionHandler

    public abstract class FileSubstitutionHandler
extends Object
implements Substitutable
    Abstract class initialize the input file for the string substitution. The sub-classes provides the way to create the Reader and Writer for the input & output file.
